data.title: Fraternity and Sorority Life
data.text: Our organization prides itself on both hosting our own philanthropic events and participating in events hosted by other members of the CSU greek community and other national organizations. We have two national philanthropies, the Sean Vernon Feliciano Amazing Day Foundation, which strives to increase awareness around mental health and decrease the rate of suicide among college students. And Donate Life, which focuses on the importance of eye and tissue donation.
